snippet.title: Dodge Spree X - Trailer
snippet.description:
Dodge Spree X is an extended edition celebrating this 1-bit platformer prototype's 11th anniversary. 

They held you captive - Time to escape from this dreaded place!
You better get moving before they come to catch you.

Available for Windows and OUYA at Itch.io:
https://samuelsousa.itch.io/

#retro #platformers #indiegame
